// inside your ViewerPage bottom bar
AnimatedScale(
  scale: _pressed ? 0.9 : 1.0,
  duration: const Duration(milliseconds: 100),
  child: IconButton(
    icon: const Icon(Icons.text_increase),
    onPressed: () {
      setState(() => _pressed = true);
      Future.delayed(const Duration(milliseconds: 100), () {
        setState(() => _pressed = false);
        _changeFontSize(2);
      });
    },
  ),
);


✅ 1. Button‑Press Animation
File: Button‑Press Animation wrap all IconButton ElevatedButton

📍 Where:
Anywhere you use IconButton or ElevatedButton, update just the icon/text child.

